N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 11.150 - Definitions

State Regulations

The term local public health educator shall mean a person who applies the principles of behavioral sciences in public health programs to foster the voluntary adaptation of behavior to improve or maintain health. Notes
